          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 text-lg">Single Dwelling Units</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Door or window required from each lower level</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Facilitates rescue and fire department access</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Critical for lower levels with heating equipment</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Not required if secondary suite exists</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold mb-3 text-lg">Multiple Units / Long Lower Levels</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Required for lower levels >25m (82 ft) long</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Minimum opening: 1100mm × 550mm</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Maximum 900mm above floor level</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Direct access to street required</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-cyan-100 rounded">
            <p class="text-sm">
              <strong>Fire Safety Note:</strong> Lower levels are high fire risk areas due to storage and heating equipment. 
              Proper egress can save lives and limit property damage. Interior stairs accessible from outdoors also satisfy this requirement.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Types of Openings -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Foundation Opening Options</h3>
          
