              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Standard Door Cut</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4">
                36" × 80" opening for basic access. Ideal for storage access or code compliance.
              </p>
              <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
                <li>✓ Single day cutting</li>
                <li>✓ Steel or fiberglass door</li>
                <li>✓ Basic waterproofing</li>
