              <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
                <li>✓ Large opening (6-12 ft)</li>
                <li>✓ Concrete stairs</li>
                <li>✓ Drainage system</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-cyan-600">From $27,000</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-100 rounded-lg p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
              <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🪟</div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-lg mb-2">Window to Door</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-4">
                Convert existing window to door opening. Most economical option.
              </p>
              <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
                <li>✓ Uses existing opening</li>
                <li>✓ Minimal excavation</li>
                <li>✓ 2-3 day completion</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-bold text-purple-600">From $6,500</p>
            </div>
