                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-amber-500 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Minimum 6" bearing on each side</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-amber-500 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Temporary support during cutting</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-amber-500 mr-2">•</span>
