                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-amber-500 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Minimum 4' from corners</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-amber-500 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Avoid utility penetrations</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-amber-500 mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Reinforcement for block walls</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
