                <li>• Sloped sill plate</li>
                <li>• Weather stripping</li>
                <li>• Threshold drainage</li>
                <li>• Caulking & sealing</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Site Grading</h4>
              <ul class="text-sm space-y-2">
                <li>• 2% slope away</li>
                <li>• Swale if needed</li>
                <li>• Downspout relocation</li>
                <li>• Surface drainage</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
